As the figure makes its way through the greenhouse foliage you desperately try to come up with a plausible excuse. The problem of course is that you’re terrible under pressure - always have been. Tests in school used to make you so nervous.. Oh come on! focus! They’re almost here. Oh yes that makes sense - it’s Mr. Cuttingsworth the Garden Club’s propagation specialist. Without waiting for him to speak you shout the first thing that comes to your mind.
